defaultpublic sector
default investment is a critical component in addressing market failures, managing risk a
defaultnd achieving technological breakthroughs, while leveraging substantial funding from the private sector or other governments. 
defaultPublicly funded programmes
default range from fully funding the most uncertain phases of primary research through to joint funding and risk
default sharing in the later stages, as technologies approach commercialisation. 
